detail.name: Black Kamehameha
detail.effect: [Activate Battle][Opponent's Turn] Choose your Leader or up to 1 of your Battle Cards and it gets +20000 power for the battle. Then, look at 3 cards from the top of your deck and place them at the top or bottom of your deck in any order.

detail.name: ブラックかめはめ波
detail.effect: [起動 戦闘中][相手のターン中]自分のリーダーか自分のバトルカード1枚までを選び、この戦闘中、パワー+20000。その後、自分のデッキの上から3枚を見て、好きな順番でデッキの上か下に置く。

faq.question: Can you use this card's [Activate Battle] skill to place 1 card at the top of your deck and 2 cards at the bottom of your deck?
faq.answer: No, you can't. After using this skill to look at 3 cards, you must place all of them at the top or all of them at the bottom of your deck in any order.

faq.question: このカードの【起動 戦闘中】によってデッキの上に1枚を上に置き、2枚を下におくことはできますか？
faq.answer: いいえ、できません。このカードのスキルで確認した3枚すべてを好きな順番でデッキの上か下に置きます。
